#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The rules of &kappname; are quite simple."
msgid "The rules of &ksudoku; are quite simple."
msgstr "&kappname; reeglid on päris lihtsad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Depending on the size of the game board, the type of puzzle and the "
#| "difficulty level chosen an individual &kappname; puzzle may take from a "
#| "few minutes to a few hours to solve."
msgid ""
"Depending on the size of the game board, the type of puzzle and the "
"difficulty level chosen an individual &ksudoku; puzzle may take from a few "
"minutes to a few hours to solve."
msgstr ""
"Sõltuvalt mängulaua suurusest, mängu tüübist ja valitud raskusastmest võib "
"iga &kappname; mängu lahendamisele kuluda mõnest minutist kuni isegi mitme "
"tunnini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each square may hold one and only one symbol."
msgstr "Igas ruudus saab olla ainult üks sümbol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each horizontal row (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol "
"exactly once."
msgstr "Igas reas tohib iga sümbolit esineda ainult üks kord."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each vertical column (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol "
"exactly once."
msgstr "Igas veerus tohib iga sümbolit esineda ainult üks kord."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each block (as defined by the game board) can contain each symbol exactly "
"once"
msgstr "Igas plokis tohib iga sümbolit esineda ainult üks kord."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193 index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Märkus:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "The set of symbols depends on the size of game you choose."
msgstr "Sümbolite valik sõltub valitud mängu suurusest."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Knowledge of mathematics or language is not required to solve &kappname; "
#| "puzzles."
msgid ""
"Knowledge of mathematics or language is not required to solve &ksudoku; "
"puzzles, but a little ability with arithmetic is needed in Killer Sudoku and "
"Mathdoku puzzles."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; mängude lahendamiseks ei ole matemaatika või keelte tundmine "
"sugugi vajalik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The symbols already on the game board when the puzzle starts cannot be "
"changed."
msgstr "Sümboleid, mis on mängu käivitades ette antud, ei saa muuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can only modify the symbols you have previously entered."
msgstr "Muuta saab ainult sümboleid, mida oled ise varem sisestanud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Puzzles generated by &kappname; have one solution only."
msgid "Puzzles generated by &ksudoku; have one solution only."
msgstr "&kappname; genereeritud mängudel on ainult üks lahendus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puzzles you enter in might have no solution or more than one solution, but "
"if they are from a published source this probably means you have made a data-"
"entry error."
msgstr ""
"Mängud, mida lood, võivad olla lahenduseta või rohkem kui ühe lahendusega, "
"aga kui nad on pärit mõnest kirjalikust allikast, on usutavam, et oled "
"sisestamisel teinud mõne vea."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kappname; Variations"
